                    💳 Pro Tip: Payment Setup & Financial Management
        <span class="pro-tip-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pro-tip-content">
                    <h4>Complete Etsy Fee Structure (2024):</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Listing Fee:</strong> $0.20 per item (lasts 4 months or until sold)</li>
                        <li><strong>Transaction Fee:</strong> 6.5% of item price + shipping cost</li>
                        <li><strong>Payment Processing:</strong> 3% + $0.25 per transaction</li>
                        <li><strong>Etsy Ads (Optional):</strong> Set daily budget, pay per click (typical: $0.20-$2.00/click)</li>
                        <li><strong>Currency Conversion:</strong> 2.5% if selling internationally in different currencies</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Pricing Formula for Profitability:</h4>
                    <p><strong>Formula:</strong> (Material Cost + Labor Cost + Overhead) × 2.5 + Etsy Fees = Minimum Price</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Materials:</strong> All supplies, packaging, shipping materials</li>
                        <li><strong>Labor:</strong> Your time × desired hourly rate (minimum $15-25/hour)</li>
                        <li><strong>Overhead:</strong> 10-20% for tools, workspace, utilities</li>
                        <li><strong>Profit Margin:</strong> 150% markup ensures sustainability</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Business Banking & Tax Setup:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Separate Business Account:</strong> Essential for clean bookkeeping and tax filing</li>
                        <li><strong>EIN (Tax ID):</strong> Get free from IRS - adds legitimacy and simplifies taxes</li>
                        <li><strong>Quarterly Taxes:</strong> Set aside 25-30% of profits for tax payments</li>
                        <li><strong>Expense Tracking:</strong> Track all business expenses for deductions</li>
                        <li><strong>Business License:</strong> Check local requirements (varies by location/product type)</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Etsy Payments Setup:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Funds deposited 1-3 business days after sale</li>
                        <li>Connect checking account (not savings) for faster transfers</li>
                        <li>Set up automatic tax document generation for year-end filing</li>
                        <li>Enable buyer protection programs for increased trust</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

