            <div class="pro-tip">
                <div class="pro-tip-header" onclick="toggleProTip(this)">
    💡 Pro Tip: [Title Here]
    <span class="pro-tip-toggle">+</span>
</div>
                <div class="pro-tip-content">
                    <h4>Photo Requirements (5-10 photos per listing):</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Main Photo:</strong> Clean white/neutral background, product centered, well-lit natural lighting</li>
                        <li><strong>Detail Shots:</strong> Close-ups of texture, craftsmanship, unique features, and quality</li>
                        <li><strong>Lifestyle Photos:</strong> Product in use, styled in a room, or being worn/used</li>
                        <li><strong>Size Reference:</strong> Show scale with hands, coins, rulers, or common objects</li>
                        <li><strong>Variations:</strong> Different colors, angles, or packaging options available</li>
                        <li><strong>Behind-the-Scenes:</strong> Your workspace, process, or you creating the item</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>SEO Title Formula That Gets Found:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Primary Keyword + Descriptors + Benefits + Style</strong></li>
                        <li>Example: "Handmade Wooden Coffee Mug Rack - Rustic Kitchen Organizer - Natural Wood Storage"</li>
                        <li>Use all 140 characters - every character counts for search visibility</li>
                        <li>Research competitor titles and Etsy search suggestions</li>
                        <li>Include gift occasions: "Perfect Gift for Coffee Lovers"</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Description Structure That Converts:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Hook (First 160 characters):</strong> Benefits-focused opening that appears in search</li>
                        <li><strong>Product Details:</strong> Materials, dimensions, colors, customization options</li>
                        <li><strong>Benefits & Uses:</strong> How it solves problems or improves the buyer's life</li>
                        <li><strong>Care Instructions:</strong> How to maintain and clean the product</li>
                        <li><strong>Shipping & Policies:</strong> processing time, packaging, return policy</li>
                        <li><strong>Call to Action:</strong> Encourage immediate purchase or contact</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>

