                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="processingAdvice" style="display: none; margin-top: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #fffaf0; border: 2px solid #ed8936; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <strong>⏰ Processing Time Impact:</strong> <span id="processingImpact">Select a processing time to see advice</span>
                </div>
            </div>
<div class="pro-tip-header" onclick="toggleProTip(this)">
    💡 Pro Tip: [Title Here]
    <span class="pro-tip-toggle">+</span>
</div>
                <div class="pro-tip-content">
                    <h4>Free Shipping Psychology (Recommended):</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Build shipping into product price:</strong> $25 item + $5 shipping = $30 item with "free" shipping</li>
                        <li><strong>Etsy search algorithm boost:</strong> Free shipping listings rank significantly higher in search results</li>
                        <li><strong>Customer preference:</strong> 90% of buyers prefer free shipping even at higher product prices</li>
                        <li><strong>International strategy:</strong> Offer free domestic shipping, charge actual rates for international</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Shipping Profiles to Create:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Small Items (under 4 oz):</strong> First-class mail, 3-5 days, $3-5</li>
                        <li><strong>Standard Items (1-13 oz):</strong> Priority mail, 1-3 days, $8-12</li>
                        <li><strong>Large/Heavy Items:</strong> Priority mail or UPS, 2-5 days, $15-25</li>
                        <li><strong>Fragile Items:</strong> Priority Express or UPS with insurance, 1-2 days, $25-40</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Processing Time Best Practices:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>1-2 business days:</strong> Ready-to-ship items, digital products, simple crafts</li>
                        <li><strong>3-5 business days:</strong> Made-to-order items, custom colors, personalization</li>
                        <li><strong>1-2 weeks:</strong> Complex custom work, seasonal high-demand periods</li>
                        <li><strong>2+ weeks:</strong> Completely custom designs, intricate handwork</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Customer Communication Tips:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Send tracking information immediately when shipped</li>
                        <li>Update customers if processing takes longer than expected</li>
                        <li>Offer expedited shipping options for urgent orders</li>
                        <li>Package items securely with branded materials when possible</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

